Harrow Vexed			KEY:Spellblight ~ Harrow Vexed							CATEGORY:Afflictions		TYPE:MinorSpellblight.Spellblight.Curse.Affliction																																																																																																																			DESC:Whenever a magic-user casts a spell, draw a harrow card. If the card is a true or partial match for the caster's alignment, the spell is cast at -2 caster levels (no added beneft for true matches). If the card is an opposite match for character's alignment, the spell is cast at +1 caster level. Otherwise, the spellblight has no effect. Restoration and lesser restoration cure this effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.15

